<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Get a quote for your custom graphic design project. Fill out our simple form to receive a price estimate.">
  <title>Get a Quote - GraphicShop</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Get a Quote</h1>
        <p>Fill out the form below to get an instant price estimate for your design project.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="quote-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="form-container">
          <form id="quoteForm" data-validate>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="designType">Design Type</label>
              <select id="designType" name="designType" required>
                <option value="">Select a design type</option>
                <option value="logo">Logo Design</option>
                <option value="icon">Icon Design</option>
                <option value="poster">Poster Design</option>
                <option value="banner">Banner Design</option>
                <option value="illustration">Illustration</option>
                <option value="other">Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="size">Size</label>
              <select id="size" name="size" required>
                <option value="">Select a size</option>
                <option value="small">Small</option>
                <option value="medium">Medium</option>
                <option value="large">Large</option>
                <option value="extra-large">Extra Large</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="price-display">
              <h3>Estimated Price</h3>
              <p class="price-amount" id="priceDisplay">$0.00</p>
              <p class="price-note">This is an estimate. Final price will be confirmed after review.</p>
            </div>

            <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="description">Project Description</label>
                <textarea id="description" name="description" placeholder="Please describe your project in detail..." required></textarea>
              </div>

              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="additionalRequirements">Additional Requirements (Optional)</label>
                <textarea id="additionalRequirements" name="additionalRequirements" placeholder="Any specific requirements or preferences..."></textarea>
              </div>

              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Submit Order</button>
            <% } else { %>
              <p class="login-prompt">Please <a href="/auth/login">log in</a> or <a href="/auth/register">register</a> to place an order.</p>

              <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Login to Continue</a>
              <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-secondary btn-full">Register Now</a>
            <% } %>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="accordion">
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <button class="accordion-header">How is the price calculated?</button>
            <div class="accordion-content">
              <p>Our pricing is based on the type of design and the size/complexity of the project. Logos typically cost more than icons, and larger sizes require more work and detail than smaller ones.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <button class="accordion-header">What if I need revisions?</button>
            <div class="accordion-content">
              <p>All our design packages include 2 rounds of revisions. If you need additional revisions beyond that, there may be additional charges based on the complexity of the changes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <button class="accordion-header">How long will my design take?</button>
            <div class="accordion-content">
              <p>Typical turnaround time is 3-7 business days, depending on the complexity of the project and our current workload. Rush services are available for an additional fee.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <button class="accordion-header">What file formats will I receive?</button>
            <div class="accordion-content">
              <p>We provide designs in multiple formats including AI, PSD, PDF, PNG, and JPG to ensure you have everything you need for both print and digital use.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/priceCalculator.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
